      "content": "idk i guess, it just feels a bit scary because it's only on one side though. my wife thinks i should go to the hospital but i really dont want to deal with the doctors and wait all night if i'm just dehydrated. u think it's really just the travel stress? i feel like if it was serious it would be more than just a tingle right?",
